modName: Leviathan Axe - God of War - DELETED
summary: Kratos"s Axe from God of War
descriptionHtml:
[b][size=5]This mod replaces The Rueful Axe with the Leviathan Axe from the newest God of War. The axe is a one-handed weapon, it has got a 30 point frost damage enchantment and base damage of the Dragonbone War Axe. You can start Clavicus Vile's daedric quest by speaking with Lod at Falkreath.[/size]
